OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776096668
OL,3,CUS and Iran end 21-hour ceasefire
OL,4,Ctalks without agreement
OL,6,FThe United States and Iran ended a
OL,7,Fhistoric round of face-to-face talks
OL,8,Fearly on Sunday without reaching an
OL,9,Fagreement, leaving the status of the
OL,10,Ffragile, two-week ceasefire unclear.
OL,12,FVice President JD Vance, who led the
OL,13,FUS delegation during the 21 hours of
OL,14,Ftalks in Pakistan's capital Islamabad,
OL,15,Fsaid negotiations finished without a
OL,16,Fdeal after the Iranians refused to
OL,17,Faccept American terms to refrain from
OL,18,Fdeveloping a nuclear weapon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776096668
OL,3,CUS and Iran end 21-hour ceasefire
OL,4,Ctalks without agreement
OL,6,FThere was no immediate comment from
OL,7,Fthe Iranian delegation, but Pakistani
OL,8,Fmediators called on both countries to
OL,9,Fmaintain the ceasefire.
OL,11,F"It is imperative that the parties
OL,12,Fcontinue to uphold their commitment to
OL,13,Fthe ceasefire," Pakistan Foreign
OL,14,FMinister Ishaq Dar said, adding that
OL,15,Fhis country will try to facilitate a
OL,16,Fnew dialogue between Iran and the U.S.
OL,17,Fin the coming days.
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
