FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776096668
OL,3,CUS and Iran end 21-hour ceasefire
OL,4,Ctalks without agreement
OL,6,FThe discussions in Islamabad began on
OL,7,FSaturday, a few days after a fragile
OL,8,Fceasefire was announced as the war
OL,9,Fthat has killed thousands of people
OL,10,Fand shaken global markets entered its
OL,11,Fseventh week.
OL,13,FVance said he remained in constant
OL,14,Fcommunication with US President Donald
OL,15,FTrump and others in the administration
OL,16,Fduring the negotiations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776096668
OL,3,CUS and Iran end 21-hour ceasefire
OL,4,Ctalks without agreement
OL,6,F"But the simple fact is that we need
OL,7,Fto see an affirmative commitment that
OL,8,Fthey will not seek a nuclear weapon,
OL,9,Fand they will not seek the tools that
OL,10,Fwould enable them to quickly achieve a
OL,11,Fnuclear weapon," Vance told reporters.
OL,13,F"That is the core goal of the
OL,14,Fpresident of the United States. And
OL,15,Fthat's what we've tried to achieve
OL,16,Fthrough these negotiations."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@PO]uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
