PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776096668
OL,3,CUS and Iran end 21-hour ceasefire
OL,4,Ctalks without agreement
OL,6,FThe vice president said he spoke with
OL,7,FTrump "a half dozen times, a dozen
OL,8,Ftimes, over the past 21 hours" and
OL,9,Falso spoke with Secretary of State
OL,10,FMarco Rubio, Treasury Secretary Scott
OL,11,FBessent and Admiral Brad Cooper, the
OL,12,Fhead of the United States Central
OL,13,FCommand.
OL,26,@oD@GOUpD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
