PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776096668
OL,3,CUS and Iran end 21-hour ceasefire
OL,4,Ctalks without agreement
OL,6,F"We were constantly in communication
OL,7,Fwith the team because we were
OL,8,Fnegotiating in good faith," Vance
OL,9,Fsaid, speaking at a podium in front of
OL,10,Fa pair of American flags with special
OL,11,Fenvoys Steve Witkoff and Jared Kushner
OL,12,Fto his side. "And we leave here, with
OL,13,Fa very simple proposal, a method of
OL,14,Funderstanding that is our final and
OL,15,Fbest offer. We'll see if the Iranians
OL,16,Faccept it."
