PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776096668
OL,3,CUS and Iran end 21-hour ceasefire
OL,4,Ctalks without agreement
OL,6,FTwo Pakistani officials, who spoke on
OL,7,Fcondition of anonymity because they
OL,8,Fwere not authorised to brief the
OL,9,Fpress, said a third round of
OL,10,Fdiscussions between the delegation
OL,11,Fheads had finished and the talks would
OL,12,Fresume after a break.
OL,14,FThen the US vice president addressed
OL,15,Fthe press, announced there was no
OL,16,Fagreement and went to the airport to
OL,17,Fleave Pakistan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
