PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776096668
OL,3,CUS and Iran end 21-hour ceasefire
OL,4,Ctalks without agreement
OL,6,FTrump had said he would suspend
OL,7,Fattacks against Iran for two weeks.
OL,8,FVance's comments did not indicate what
OL,9,Fwill happen after that time period
OL,10,Fexpires or if the ceasefire will
OL,11,Fremain in place.
OL,13,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,14,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,15,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,16,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
